{include file='before_body.phtml' title='找回密码'}
<body>

<div class="zh_top">
  <div class="main">
    <a class="fl" href="{url('')}"><img src="{$tpldir}/images/logo.png"></a>
    <span class="fr"><a href="{url('')}">返回首页 &gt;&gt;</a></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main zh_content" {if $step !== 'step1'}hidden{/if}>
  <div class="title">填写用户名</div>
  <div class="icon_zh_1"></div>
<form action="{url('user/forgot')}" method="POST" id="login-form">
  <div class="content">
    <p class="app"><input type="text" name="username" value="{$smarty.post.username|default:""}" class="btnTEXT" placeholder="用户名">{if isset($msg) && $msg != ''}<em><i class="cha"></i>{$msg}</em>{/if}</p>
    <p><input type="submit" value="发送邮件" class="btnBUTTON"></p>
  </div>
</form>
</div>
<div class="main zh_content" {if $step !== 'step2'}hidden{/if} >
  <div class="title">验证身份</div>
  <div class="icon_zh_2"></div>
  <div class="contet2">
    <p>我们已将“[ <span>{$username|default:""}</span>账户 ] 找回密码”发送到您的邮箱</p>
    <p>{$email|default:""}中，请在尽快收信重置密码。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="contet2_b">
    <p>还没收到验证邮件？</p>
    <p>尝试到广告、垃圾邮件目录里找找看，或者  <a href="{url('user/forgot')}">重新发送</a>  找回密码邮件</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="main zh_bottom">
  <div class="cory">{$config->get('footer', '')}</div>
</div>
</body>
{include file='after_body.phtml'}
<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function() {
  $('.btnBUTTON').click(function(e){
    var username = $('[name="username"]').val();
    $('.app').find('em').remove();
    if (username == '') {
      $('.app').append('<em><i class="cha"></i>用户名不能为空</em>');
      e.preventDefault();
    };
  });
});
</script>
</html>
